# Design core (task.skarpa.dev)

Read `design/DIRECTIVE.md` before visual or IA changes.

- Low cognitive load: homepage is **today only**
- Terminology: **task**, never todo
- WCAG 2.1 AA; keyboard and visible focus
- Token-based spacing and type; no ad-hoc palettes
- **Light and dark mode:** define tokens in `layout.css`; use semantic Tailwind colors; test both modes on every UI change
- shadcn-svelte + Tailwind only; no new UI libraries
- Emphasis via `**text**` in JSON, rendered by `EmphasisText`
- Close day requires double confirm in UI; skills use `POST /api/day/close`
